    dc:description "Figures 1–10. Line drawings of Dactylogyrus pisolabrae n. sp. (drawings are of the holotype, HWML 216232, unless otherwise specified). (1) Whole mount (ventral). (2) Dorsal anchor. (3) Dorsal bar. (4) Ventral anchor (4A). (5) Ventral bar. (6) Hook. (7) Male copulatory organ. (8) Accessory piece. (9) Male copulatory organ (HWML 216233). (10) Accessory piece (HWML 216233)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7746692/files/figure.png" ;
